      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior boasts a flawless factory finish with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the interior remains in showroom state with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives like a brand-new car, complete with all original documentation and accessories.",
