    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This specimen remains in pristine condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From its flawless exterior finish to its untouched interior appointments, this automobile offers an unrivaled driving experience for the discerning enthusiast. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this benchmark of quality.",
      "price": 46500.0,
