    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream. This car is in truly stunning, showroom-level shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve meticulously babied it, keeping it garage-kept and spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready to hit the road today, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD, a pinnacle of 90s JDM engineering. This specimen features the 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, maintaining exceptional compression across all rotor faces with a seamless transition at 4,500 RPM. The chassis is structurally pristine, retaining its factory-spec 50:50 weight distribution and lightweight aluminum double-wishbone suspension. Power is delivered through a precise five-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring surgical corner exit. The cooling system has been meticulously maintained to prevent thermal degradation, and the vacuum line assembly remains supple and leak-free. A turn-key investment for the purist seeking mechanical perfection and uncompromised performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    }
